{"tid":1984632,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭月娥：呼籲企業及市民在DSE核心科目考試日，採用彈性時間上班","createTime":"2020-04-22T14:48:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T09:07:29.000Z","uid":212626,"like":9,"dislike":344,"uniUserReply":109,"replies":[{"pid":"46d9797edf02b6cda26da6f6bb07a34fd0ce1739","tid":1984632,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:48:03.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥指，現在距離中學文憑試開考只有兩天，而確診個案已經近十天停留在個位數字，考試應該可以安全、順利地進行，<span style=\"color: red;\">又呼籲企業及市民在核心科目的考試日，即是下周一至周三，以及5月2日、4日和5日，盡可能採用彈性時間上班，避開早上6時半至8時的繁忙時間，讓考生前往試場時交通更為順暢</span>。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥在社交網站貼文，指教育局、考評局和將用作試場的學校，都已經做好防疫措施，而港鐵及巴士公司亦已經宣布會在考試期間的早上加密班次，便利考生赴考，又呼籲考生注意個人衛生，出門戴口罩、勤洗手等。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1282680&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1282680%26csid%3D261_341&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6Cqd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=60258430\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1282680&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"2b5912aa81ca642623724a4e86dc960c352d4999","tid":1984632,"uid":177089,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:49:49.000Z","msg":"無撚腦"},{"pid":"d54090d57a7533843f75c1af1eca1093c736814c","tid":1984632,"uid":37874,"like":423,"dislike":2,"score":421,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:49:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"928befec45ea4b8479daf41ba676566977898429","tid":1984632,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:50:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i